  "general_provisions": "This bill establishes the Nuclear Energy Regulatory Office within the Division of Waste Management and Radiation Control.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>establishes the Nuclear Energy Regulatory Office within the Division of Waste Management and Radiation Control;<hr><ltbullet>grants rulemaking authority to the division for nuclear energy regulation;<hr><ltbullet>authorizes establishment and collection of fees for nuclear energy licensing and oversight;<hr><ltbullet>directs the division to pursue expanded Agreement State status with the United States Nuclear Regulatory Commission;<hr><ltbullet>authorizes the director to enter cooperative agreements with federal agencies; and<hr><ltbullet>authorizes new positions for the Nuclear Energy Regulatory Office.",
